content: I bought a laptop from Best Buy for $800, a kitchen appliance set from Macy's, a cozy throw blanket from Target, some tops and jeans from H&M, skincare products from Sephora, a coffee maker and notecards from Amazon, handmade jewelry and candles from a holiday market, a personalized photo album from Shutterfly, slippers from UGG, toilet paper and laundry detergent from Walmart, dresses and boots from Nordstrom, discounted designer clothing from an outlet mall, a fitness tracker from Fitbit, and kitchen utensils from Sur La Table.
